#eNCA reporter Heidi Giokos met up with award-winning American comedian and television host, Steve Harvey, to speak about his journey in the media industry. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - A king of comedy, successful TV host and known for his sharp tongue, Steve Harvey is not your average. His brand is extending to South Africa, with the popular American game show, Family Feud hitting our shores. The show pits two families against each other to win cash and prizes. READ: Steve Harvey Show presents four-year-old worship leader Fanatics of the show will be pleased to know it's launching in the country early next year. eNCA Business reporter Heidi Giokos met up with the award-winner to talk about his long journey in the industry and his plans for Mzansi. Watch the full interview above.